5
00:00:11.279 --> 00:00:14.720
One word from Mr. Edwards, and we're all done.

6
00:00:14.720 --> 00:00:17.760
Miss Ewing, he must have fooled you too.

7
00:00:17.760 --> 00:00:20.800
He forged the president's signature. He tricked all of us.

8
00:00:20.800 --> 00:00:22.160
Don't bother to his trap.

9
00:00:23.600 --> 00:00:27.359
