12
00:00:40.929 --> 00:00:42.799
It's there. It's really there.

13
00:00:43.359 --> 00:00:48.799
And soon the website will be updated with you and your father have been fired and arrested,

14
00:00:48.799 --> 00:00:51.920
or we can make sure it gets grounded in obituary.

15
00:00:51.920 --> 00:00:52.719
Your choice.

16
00:00:52.719 --> 00:00:54.079
Mr. Edwards.

17
00:00:54.079 --> 00:00:58.159
Now, Farrah, if you hadn't arrived when you did, I wouldn't be able to witness such

18
00:00:58.159 --> 00:01:01.840
wonderful performances, because the auto plant has managed to

19
00:01:01.840 --> 00:01:05.280
breed such corrupt and power abusing parasites,

20
00:01:05.280 --> 00:01:08.560
even the idiot like him, and be a researcher.

21
00:01:08.560 --> 00:01:10.719
You know, I think it's time we clean house.

22
00:01:10.719 --> 00:01:11.760
I agree.

23
00:01:11.760 --> 00:01:15.780
I think it's time we clean house.

24
00:01:15.780 --> 00:01:17.219
I can explain to you.

25
00:01:17.219 --> 00:01:20.340
No, actually, I think you understood everything pretty well.

26
00:01:20.340 --> 00:01:29.250
No! No! No! No! No! No! No! Please! Please!

27
00:01:29.250 --> 00:01:31.730
You know, nobody's listening to your bullshit.

28
00:01:31.730 --> 00:01:34.209
And frankly, I'm not interested in it.

29
00:01:39.439 --> 00:01:43.680
See that? Every man acts tough when there's a gun put in his face,

30
00:01:43.680 --> 00:01:45.920
