33
00:01:54.879 --> 00:01:56.239
Yes, president.

34
00:01:56.239 --> 00:01:58.480
Gentlemen, can you please take our guest away?

35
00:01:58.480 --> 00:02:02.769
No! No! No! No! No! No!

36
00:02:02.769 --> 00:02:05.650
Gentlemen, tell us.

37
00:02:05.650 --> 00:02:08.819
